      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about like, getting drunk or anything. just like a small glass, maybe 5oz. i feel like a little bit of alcohol actually helps me unwind and get into that sleepy headspace. wouldn't a tiny bit just make the med work a little more effectively without being like, super dangerous?",
